ique para visualizar o currículo" href="http://lattes.cnpq.br/5297252436860003" target="_blank" tabindex="252">GUIZZARDI, G.</a> . Ontological Analysis and Redesign of Security Modeling in ArchiMate. In: IFIP Working Conference on The Practice of Enterprise Modeling, 2022, London. The Practice of Enterprise Modeling. Cham: Springer, 2022. v. 456. p. 82-98. </span></div><br class="clear"><br class="clear"><div class="layout-cell layout-cell-1 text-align-right"><div class="layout-cell-pad-6 text-align-right"><b>19. </b></div></div><div class="layout-cell layout-cell-11"><span class="transform">OLIVEIRA, J. B. ; <b>ALMEIDA, J. P. A.</b> ; ZAMBON, EDUARDO ; <a class="tooltip" title="Clique para visualizar o currículo" href="http://lattes.cnpq.br/5297252436860003" target="_blank" tabindex="253">GUIZZARDI, G.</a> . Building Correct Taxonomies with a Well-Founded Graph Grammar. In: Research Challenges in Information Science. RCIS 2021, 2021, Virtual. Research Challenges in Information Science. RCIS 2021. LNBIP. Cham: Springer, 2021. v. 415. p. 506-522. </span></div><br class="clear"><br class="clear"><div class="layout-cell layout-cell-1 text-align-right"><div class="layout-cell-pad-6 text-align-right"><b>20. </b></div></div><div class="layout-cell layout-cell-11"><span class="transform">GUIDONI, G. ; <b>ALMEIDA, J. P. A.</b> ; <a class="tooltip" title="Clique para visualizar o currículo" href="http://lattes.cnpq.br/5297252436860003" target="_blank" tabindex="254">GUIZZARDI, G.</a> . Forward Engineering Relational Schemas and High-Level Data Access from Conceptual Models. In: 40th International Conference on Conceptual Modeling (ER 2021), 2021, St. John's. 40th International Conference on Conceptual Modeling (ER 2021). Cham: Springer, 2021. </span></div><br class="clear"><br class="clear"><div class="layout-cell layout-cell-1 text-align-right"><div class="layout-cell-pad-6 text-align-right"><b>21. </b></div></div><div class="layout-cell layout-cell-11"><span class="transfo